QueryText: Pradhan Mantri Kisan Maan Dhan Yojana (PM-KMY) ?
KccAns:
Pradhan Mantri Kisan Maan Dhan Yojana (PM-KMY) -- The problem is
compounded in respect of small and marginal farmers as they have minimal or no savings
to provide for old age. The Pradhan Mantri Kisan Maan-Dhan Yojana (PM-KMY) provides
for an assured monthly pension of Rs. 3000/- to all land holding Small and Marginal
Farmers (SMFs), whether male or female, on their attaining the age of 60 years.
